The brand new iteration of LW.

Docker:
  Install:
    `curl -fsSL "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/GanerCodes/LWMP/refs/heads/main/Docker/man" | bash`
    Notes:
      if $PWD contains a dir called "Preset", it is added as the "Docker" preset
      if $PWD contains a file called "CERT.pem", it sets the cert to it
  Flash:
    `./manage y`
  Server:
    `./manage s`

(More info will go here at some point as well as fixing various jank)